{"tid":2059803,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有興趣買保險既手足入一入來","createTime":"2020-06-11T07:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T13:33:05.000Z","uid":34163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"92937dc75ffdf0f696f6af78d4e340e0a78cb161","tid":2059803,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:32:53.000Z","msg":"成日話黃色經濟圈<br />\n被捕手足其實根本冇得益<br />\n得益既只係個堆有連儂牆既餐廳<br />\n雖然餐廳佢地咁做係有風險<br />\n但係我完全見唔到有幾多資源落返手足到<br />\n好多黃店其實都係自己賺自己袋<br />\n我之前返過兩間黃店都係自己賺自己笑<br />\n<br />\n如果有興趣幫下我朋友既就telegram搵佢<br />\n被人charge緊暴動<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/letheryo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fletheryo&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRHfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=15b6a995\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/letheryo</a>"},{"pid":"a9bc489b352c7d130ecbd4b8ddf53b8d94f2e80c","tid":2059803,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:35:53.000Z","msg":"最諷刺嘅係 為場運動付出最多嘅失去最多 咩都唔理嘅港豬生活得更加愉快<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2059253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2059253</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b3d71c67460dbabc74d3aeaded6dc05e59c4511b","tid":2059803,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:46:27.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"3b106e89d9be5d81ce54f86ba156b730dd6e3b81","tid":2059803,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:46:40.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"884b4327576024d74a493c6941860771acb04228","tid":2059803,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:46:50.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"eacb9bba763518f3fe0bfab1a7497d69c62aa39b","tid":2059803,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:47:00.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"ad152988e8882ad651e07583ad4bd20ffa9df7b5","tid":2059803,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:47:11.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"df97613